Foreleg
(Fig. 
3a-c
). 
Femur
with dense row of curved, spine-like setae on dorsal margin, on apex short, stout setae on anterior and posterior side; femoral patch absent; 
tibia
with patellotibial suture, dorsal margin with row of medium, clavate setae; 
